            <note xml:id="foot.f2">The sketch has not been found. The dog in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_2400.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Expression</hi></ref>, p. 53, fig. 6, has its head tilted up.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-8339.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to Briton Riviere, 19 May [1872]</ref> and n. 3. Riviere refers to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1312.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Elinor Mary Bonham-Carter</ref>; see also <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1581.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi></ref> vol. 19, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7833.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from Briton Riviere to E. M. Bonham-Carter, 26 June 1871</ref>.</note>
